snippet.title: Faz Plays - Kubo 1 & 2 (Indie / Evercade)(Gameplay) - Evercade VS Secret Game
snippet.description:
Recorded on original hardware via ELGATO game capture HD

**************************************************************************

Welcome to the Gamesroom. My main aim with this channel was initially to create a Gameplay database from all the games in my personal collection. All footage is recorded from official releases (Physical, Digital & compilations) via an Elgato Game Capture HD on original hardware. As time goes on, I hope to have a wide range of popular & lesser known games showcased on here from various consoles.

I used to do a lot of WWE 2K content too, but I have shifted that over to my 2nd channel which can be found here:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgUAKD8XxjeTlgbwiqYeM5g

**********************
